<body>
   <p><strong>Add / Edit Users</strong></p>
<p>This screen will allow you to add a new User or edit an existing User</p>

<p>Enter / Edit the details: Name, Email Address, Password & Confirm the entered Password, Phone Number, Select the Organization to which the User belongs, Select the Role for the User</p>

<p>Select the Status of the User (Active / Deactive) and click on the Save Button to save the User details</p>

<p>To delete the User select the User and click on the Delete button</p>

</body>
